===================================================
examples:
).extract .aac from .mp4 [ in $folder ]
).extract ado from .mp4 [ in $folder ]
).extract vdo from .flv [ in $folder ]
).extract all from vdo [ in $folder ]
).merge ado vdo to .mp4 [ in $folder ]
).merge vdo .m4a to .flv [ in $folder ]
).convert .flv to .mp4 [ in $folder ]
).convert abc.flv to .mp4 [ in $folder ]
).convert abc.flv to fucker.mp4 [ in $folder ]
).convert ado, vdo to .mp3 [ in $folder ]
===================================================
references:
).https://github.com/flagbug/FlvExtract.git
).https://github.com/gpac/gpac.git
).git://git.code.sf.net/p/sox/code
